analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: Neutral regime persists amid tariff-risk ablation. The GMS score of 52 dictates a transitionary stance as the fiscal-monetary nexus stabilizes following the judicial invalidation of protectionist trade barriers. While liquidity convexity remains supportive and VIX compression signals volatility mean reversion, the stagnation in copper-gold vectors and negative sentiment divergence mandate tactical restraint. Credit spread expansion in high-yield tranches offsets equity appreciation. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

reports.EN: Neutral regime persists amid tariff-risk ablation. The GMS score of 52 dictates a transitionary stance as the fiscal-monetary nexus stabilizes following the judicial invalidation of protectionist trade barriers. While liquidity convexity remains supportive and VIX compression signals volatility mean reversion, the stagnation in copper-gold vectors and negative sentiment divergence mandate tactical restraint. Credit spread expansion in high-yield tranches offsets equity appreciation. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.ES: Rgimen neutral persiste tras ablacin de aranceles. El GMS de 52 dicta una postura transicional mientras el nexo fiscal-monetario se estabiliza tras la invalidacin judicial de las barreras proteccionistas. Aunque la convexidad de la liquidez ofrece soporte y la compresin del VIX seala una reversin a la media de volatilidad, el estancamiento en los vectores cobre/oro y la divergencia del sentimiento cripto exigen restriccin tctica. La expansin de spreads compensa la apreciacin. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.ID: Rezim netral bertahan di tengah penghapusan risiko tarif. Skor GMS 52 mendikte sikap transisi saat neksus fiskal-moneter stabil pasca pembatalan yudisial terhadap hambatan proteksionis. Meskipun konveksitas likuiditas tetap mendukung dan kompresi VIX mensinyalkan pembalikan rata-rata volatilitas, stagnasi vektor tembaga/emas dan divergensi sentimen kripto menuntut penahanan taktis. Ekspansi spread kredit pada segmen high-yield mengimbangi apresiasi ekuitas, sehingga diperlukan disiplin. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.DE: Neutrales Regime verharrt trotz Zollrisiko-Ablation. Der GMS-Score von 52 diktiert eine bergangshaltung, whrend sich der fiskalisch-monetre Nexus nach der gerichtlichen Aufhebung protektionistischer Hrden stabilisiert. Whrend Liquidittskonvexitt sttzt und die VIX-Kompression eine Volatilitts-Mean-Reversion signalisiert, erzwingen stagnierende Kupfer-Gold-Vektoren und eine negative Sentiment-Divergenz taktische Zurckhaltung. Die Ausweitung der Credit Spreads kompensiert die Asset-Appreziation. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.FR: Le rgime neutre persiste malgr l'ablation des tarifs. Le score GMS de 52 impose une posture de transition alors que le lien fiscaux-montaire se stabilise suite  l'invalidation judiciaire des barrires protectionnistes. Bien que la convexit de la liquidit reste favorable et que la compression du VIX signale un retour  la moyenne de la volatilit, la stagnation des vecteurs cuivre-or et la divergence du sentiment crypto exigent une retenue tactique. L'largissement des spreads crdit compense l'apprciation. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
